caption.text:
We are very happy to announce that Indonesia Debate Open is back and open for registration. Details of IDO 2017 are as follows:

INDONESIA DEBATE OPEN 2017
(PRE-ABP TOURNAMENT)

Dates: 15-17 SEP 2017 (Fri-Sun)
Venue: Jakarta, Indonesia

Institution: Prasetiya Mulya University (Host of Asian BP 2016)

Co-CA: James Leeder (Sydney)

Co-CA: Ashish Kumar (Cambridge)

DCAs: •Lee Chin Wee (Oxford) •Kenneth Kang (NUS) •Nicolo Fortuna (Ateneo) •Fadhilah Fitri (Universitas Indonesia)

Convenor: Andre Kua & Ernest W. Silanoe

Tournament: 6 Prelim Rounds, 4 Outrounds, WUDC Format

Team cap: 80 teams 
Reg Fee: 500,000 IDR/Person (Appro. 37 USD)

Adj Rule: N-1

Meals: Lunch & Dinner on All 3 Days
Socials: Excursion on Day 01
Break Night Party: Clubbing Night! Sultan Hotel or equivalent!

Transport: Between social venues and university

3-Nights Hotel: To be confirmed

Register: http://bit.ly/2vCJ369

#IndonesiaDebateOpen2017
#IDO2017
